# SPA fallback: serve index.html (200, a rewrite -- URL is preserved) for any
# path without a real file, so react-router handles client-side routes. Without
# this, deep links and page refreshes on sub-routes (e.g. /docs, /security) 404
# on a static host. Vite copies public/ into the build output, so this lands at
# dist/_redirects where Cloudflare Pages reads it.
/*    /index.html   200
